{"tid":1932433,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[民主黨 又發功] 涂 謹 申 : 沒 有 見 到 任 何 跡 象 顯 示 武 警 在 港 採 取 執 法 行 動","createTime":"2020-03-18T17:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T20:33:06.000Z","uid":219007,"like":7,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b9e959c1b0c4c8126bda568341d296a8bb548d37","tid":1932433,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T17:20:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE%E5%BC%95%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-4-000-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%A6%E8%AD%A6%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E6%B8%AF-%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2580%258F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-4-000-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%2F&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=5a141c85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2580%258F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-4-000-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%2F&h=c4a630bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE%E5%BC%95%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-4-000-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%A6%E8%AD%A6%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E6%B8%AF-%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95/</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社引述外交消息指，在去年香港反送中運動期間，中國武警曾經參與香港警方的前線工作（joined Hong Kong police on the frontlines），到現場觀察抗爭運動。消息指，香港警方曾經帶武警監視抗爭者及其戰術，以加深對香港局勢的了解。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">路透社引述外交官估計，曾經到香港的武警多達 4,000 人。報道亦引述民主黨立法會議員涂謹申稱，留意到有香港警察帶武警走上前線，似乎是為了擔任觀察的工作。報道指涂謹申及外交官員消息，都沒有見到任何跡象顯示武警在港採取執法行動，或是執行觀察以外的工作。</span><br />\n<br />\n中國國防部回覆路透社查詢時，稱武警部隊並沒有進駐香港。而香港警務處發言人亦否認報道，稱沒有任何內地執法部門曾經到訪或進行觀察。國務院新聞辦公室及中聯辦皆沒有回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述多個外交消息指，解放軍駐港部隊去年亦擴充至 12,000 人。武警雖然與解放軍共用設施，但擁有自己的車輛，包括是兩棲裝甲運兵車及推土機等。<br />\n<br />\n去年 9 月，路透社已引述外國使節消息指，駐港解放軍人數倍增，駐港解放軍具有防暴配備，使節形容行動是「解放軍在港有史以來最大規模集結」。報道亦指武警混入其中，相信北京鎮壓香港示威將會派遣武警打頭陣。<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話冇證據證明但有片段見到令人懷疑都正常<br />\n咩叫 '都沒有見到任何跡象顯示武警在港採取執法行動，或是執行觀察以外的工作' <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDLLM民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b48e17bc183f4544f0f9449ba78163cbcf4e78d","tid":1932433,"uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"涂謹申說，「我留意到香港警員帶中國保安部隊到示威前線，顯然扮演觀察角色」，有理由相信中國部隊包括駐守香港的武警。該名要求保持匿名的外交官也說，香港警員曾陪同中國武警到前線。<br />\n<br />\n中國國防部回應路透社提問時說，武警並未在香港駐守，香港警方發言人則說他們「強調沒有任何內地執法機關的成員進行這種訪問或觀察」。國務院新聞辦公室和香港中聯辦都未回應提問。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200318/SKVPK6BF3PX7BNMIVSCMCS347Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200318%2FSKVPK6BF3PX7BNMIVSCMCS347Q%2F&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=3f7e4000\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200318%2FSKVPK6BF3PX7BNMIVSCMCS347Q%2F&h=fe693566\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200318/SKVPK6BF3PX7BNMIVSCMCS347Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報係咪報啲唔報啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951c006fc5e28c2ed1feef24410c66ed662ad49e","tid":1932433,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T17:23:25.000Z","msg":"佢咁講先聰明呀，表面上幫政府說話，但認同咗有武警上前線"},{"pid":"c04d915339ba85c43b5da48b60eb59ce299e4578","tid":1932433,"uid":22047,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T17:26:21.000Z","msg":"樓主，泛民係呢到唔屌得架，我掩護你，走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146e934cf116fe86f113e2c7da6298138a65aa88","tid":1932433,"uid":316048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T17:27:25.000Z","msg":"曲直難分"},{"pid":"c3c4a7ebcbe46a2d3823418ca38724dbebf9c8c9","tid":1932433,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T17:30:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">報道亦引述民主黨立法會議員涂謹申稱，留意到有香港警察帶武警走上前線，似乎是為了擔任觀察的工作。</span>報道指涂謹申及外交官員消息，都沒有見到任何跡象顯示武警在港採取執法行動，或是執行觀察以外的工作。"},{"pid":"dd90ab8a4834bfd38469b36598b121e30be3319e","tid":1932433,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T17:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2d53042b3febb3c35cf151d9fd0f1cfb4bbb39","tid":1932433,"uid":107297,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T17:30:22.000Z","msg":"雖然咁講冇錯<